name: Selasar_Imajinasi Tarot #IV “The Emperor”
description:
IV - L'Empereur
It is one of the 22 Major Arcana
by Selasar Imajinasi.

The emperor is ascending the throne!!! Even though he looks funny, he is a figure who is able to control and guide everything. He was enjoying a state where all was peaceful and serene under his leadership.
